            <title><![CDATA[Disney And Starbucks Have A $50 Collab That May Not Suck]]></title>
            <link>https://kotaku.com/starbucks-disney-minnie-mouse-cups-stanley-quenchers-1851737678</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/disney-and-starbucks-have-a-50-collab-that-may-not-suck.1079940/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[https://kotaku.com/starbucks-disney-minnie-mouse-cups-stanley-quenchers-1851737678<br/><br/><div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div><p>Starbucks is looking to <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://qz.com/starbucks-new-items-value-wars-mcdonalds-2025-1851733465&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://qz.com/starbucks-new-items-value-wars-mcdonalds-2025-1851733465" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">reignite consumer interest</a></span> by teaming up with Disney for a limited-edition Minnie Mouse-themed collection. </p><div><h4>Suggested Reading</h4></div><div data-video-id="194664" data-monetizable="true" data-position="sidebar" data-video-title="Disney's New Post-Apocalyptic Anime Proves The Mouse Has Good Taste" data-video-blog-id="9" data-video-network="kotaku" data-video-duration="162" data-playlist="194664,193897,196115" data-current="194664"><div><p>Disney's New Post-Apocalyptic Anime Proves The Mouse Has Good Taste</p></div><video disablepictureinpicture="" muted="" playsinline="" width="100%" height="100%" crossorigin="anonymous" preload="none"><source data-src="https://vid.kinja.com/prod/194664/194664_240p.mp4" label="240p" type="video/mp4"><source data-src="https://vid.kinja.com/prod/194664/194664_480p.mp4" label="480p" type="video/mp4"><source data-src="https://vid.kinja.com/prod/194664/194664_720p.mp4" label="720p" type="video/mp4"><source data-src="https://vid.kinja.com/prod/194664/194664_1080p.mp4" label="1080p" type="video/mp4"><track kind="captions" label="English" src="https://kinja.com/api/videoupload/caption/20130.vtt" srclang="en"></video><div><ul><li data-label="">Off</li><li data-label="English">English</li></ul></div></div><div><h4>Suggested Reading</h4></div><p>The 24-ounce stainless steel cold cup, priced at <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://www.disneystore.com/minnie-mouse-stainless-steel-starbucks-tumbler-with-straw-walt-disney-world-433133581380.html?cjdata=MXxOfDB8WXww&amp;LSID=100103763|15734611|126006X1587338X0a8cc9ddc9a2417fb33a1dcab6a91a65&amp;CMP=AFL-AffLSGen_Content_5370367_15734611&amp;att=LSGenAffl&amp;EFC=224510&amp;cjevent=cd68e550cd2411ef808b76c70a82b832&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://www.disneystore.com/minnie-mouse-stainless-steel-starbucks-tumbler-with-straw-walt-disney-world-433133581380.html?cjdata=MXxOfDB8WXww&amp;LSID=100103763|15734611|126006X1587338X0a8cc9ddc9a2417fb33a1dcab6a91a65&amp;CMP=AFL-AffLSGen_Content_5370367_15734611&amp;att=LSGenAffl&amp;EFC=224510&amp;cjevent=cd68e550cd2411ef808b76c70a82b832" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">$45</a></span>, features a satin red metallic base, white polka dots, and Minnie’s face. Alongside the cold cup, Starbucks is also offering a <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://www.disneystore.com/minnie-mouse-icon-stainless-steel-travel-tumbler-with-straw-plus-zip-case-433113582451.html?cjdata=MXxOfDB8WXww&amp;isProductSearch=1&amp;searchType=regular&amp;LSID=100103763|15734611|126006X1587338X040a0b91a6f928de7e9606889e1be943&amp;CMP=AFL-AffLSGen_Content_5370367_15734611&amp;att=LSGenAffl&amp;EFC=224510&amp;cjevent=0fff0486cd2511ef808a11160a82b839&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://www.disneystore.com/minnie-mouse-icon-stainless-steel-travel-tumbler-with-straw-plus-zip-case-433113582451.html?cjdata=MXxOfDB8WXww&amp;isProductSearch=1&amp;searchType=regular&amp;LSID=100103763|15734611|126006X1587338X040a0b91a6f928de7e9606889e1be943&amp;CMP=AFL-AffLSGen_Content_5370367_15734611&amp;att=LSGenAffl&amp;EFC=224510&amp;cjevent=0fff0486cd2511ef808a11160a82b839" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">$50</a></span> Minnie Mouse Steel Travel Tumbler, which bears a striking resemblance to Stanley’s popular Quenchers.</p><p>This move comes as Starbucks grapples with <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://qz.com/starbucks-q3-2024-us-china-demand-weakens-1851609406?_gl=1*p3561z*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzc5MTMuNjAuMC4w&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://qz.com/starbucks-q3-2024-us-china-demand-weakens-1851609406?_gl=1*p3561z*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzc5MTMuNjAuMC4w" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">slowing sales growth</a></span> and <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://qz.com/starbucks-refreshers-coffee-brian-niccol-coffee-1851675411?_gl=1*p3561z*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzc5MTMuNjAuMC4w&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://qz.com/starbucks-refreshers-coffee-brian-niccol-coffee-1851675411?_gl=1*p3561z*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzc5MTMuNjAuMC4w" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">rising competition</a></span>. While the nostalgic tie-up with Disney might generate some buzz, it’s <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://qz.com/starbucks-strike-christmas-pay-raise-labor-amazon-1851726088?_gl=1*p3561z*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzc5MTMuNjAuMC4w&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://qz.com/starbucks-strike-christmas-pay-raise-labor-amazon-1851726088?_gl=1*p3561z*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzc5MTMuNjAuMC4w" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">unlikely to address</a></span> the <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://qz.com/starbucks-in-office-mandate-or-quit-amazon-dell-walmart-1851683336?_gl=1*p3561z*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzc5MTMuNjAuMC4w&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://qz.com/starbucks-in-office-mandate-or-quit-amazon-dell-walmart-1851683336?_gl=1*p3561z*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzc5MTMuNjAuMC4w" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">underlying challenges</a></span> the <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://qz.com/starbucks-strike-locations-christmas-1851727460?_gl=1*p3561z*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzc5MTMuNjAuMC4w&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://qz.com/starbucks-strike-locations-christmas-1851727460?_gl=1*p3561z*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzc5MTMuNjAuMC4w" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">brand is facing</a></span>. </p><p>Starbucks’ new CEO, Brian Niccol, has <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://qz.com/starbucks-menu-items-drinks-cut-brian-niccol-oleato-1851687207?_gl=1*p3561z*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzc5MTMuNjAuMC4w&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://qz.com/starbucks-menu-items-drinks-cut-brian-niccol-oleato-1851687207?_gl=1*p3561z*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzc5MTMuNjAuMC4w" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">vowed</a></span> to <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://qz.com/starbucks-ceo-brian-niccol-retail-consumer-q4-2024-1851679223?_gl=1*p3561z*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzc5MTMuNjAuMC4w&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://qz.com/starbucks-ceo-brian-niccol-retail-consumer-q4-2024-1851679223?_gl=1*p3561z*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzc5MTMuNjAuMC4w" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">return the company</a></span> to its <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://qz.com/starbucks-changes-ceo-brian-niccol-analysts-1851696533?_gl=1*1wan155*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzc5MTMuNjAuMC4w&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://qz.com/starbucks-changes-ceo-brian-niccol-analysts-1851696533?_gl=1*1wan155*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzc5MTMuNjAuMC4w" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">roots</a></span> by focusing on <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://qz.com/starbucks-turnaround-plan-ceo-brian-niccol-1851686795?_gl=1*1wan155*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzc5MTMuNjAuMC4w&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://qz.com/starbucks-turnaround-plan-ceo-brian-niccol-1851686795?_gl=1*1wan155*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzc5MTMuNjAuMC4w" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">speed and simplicity</a></span>. Niccol has <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://qz.com/starbucks-q4-2024-linear-tv-ads-agronomists-baristas-1851686255&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://qz.com/starbucks-q4-2024-linear-tv-ads-agronomists-baristas-1851686255" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">committed</a></span> to making <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://qz.com/starbucks-ceo-brian-niccol-coffee-menu-pare-down-retail-1851690763?_gl=1*1diu0*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzc5OTAuNjAuMC4w&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://qz.com/starbucks-ceo-brian-niccol-coffee-menu-pare-down-retail-1851690763?_gl=1*1diu0*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzc5OTAuNjAuMC4w" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">coffee in under four minutes</a></span>,  <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://qz.com/starbucks-cuts-olive-oil-oleato-beverage-brian-niccol-1851684549&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://qz.com/starbucks-cuts-olive-oil-oleato-beverage-brian-niccol-1851684549" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">paring down the menu</a></span> to make ordering more efficient, and <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://qz.com/starbucks-q4-2024-non-dairy-charges-condiment-bar-chang-1851685647?_gl=1*46vv1a*_ga*NjQwMDk3NjE0LjE3MTMxODc3NjE.*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI3NjcxNy4xMDIuMS4xNzM2Mjc5Mjk1LjU1LjAuMA..&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://qz.com/starbucks-q4-2024-non-dairy-charges-condiment-bar-chang-1851685647?_gl=1*46vv1a*_ga*NjQwMDk3NjE0LjE3MTMxODc3NjE.*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI3NjcxNy4xMDIuMS4xNzM2Mjc5Mjk1LjU1LjAuMA.." target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">removing the upcharge</a></span> for non-dairy milk alternatives. However, whether these steps can spur growth and <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://qz.com/starbucks-money-hiring-new-workers-brian-niccol-retail-1851676553?_gl=1*kobuln*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzgwMDYuNDQuMC4w&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://qz.com/starbucks-money-hiring-new-workers-brian-niccol-retail-1851676553?_gl=1*kobuln*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzgwMDYuNDQuMC4w" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">weather</a></span> the <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://qz.com/21-states-raise-minimum-wage-inflation-1851731661?_gl=1*kobuln*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzgwMDYuNDQuMC4w&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://qz.com/21-states-raise-minimum-wage-inflation-1851731661?_gl=1*kobuln*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzgwMDYuNDQuMC4w" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">broader economic pressures</a></span> – such as <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://qz.com/cpi-consumer-price-index-inflation-federal-reserve-1851716425?_gl=1*kobuln*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzgwMDYuNDQuMC4w&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://qz.com/cpi-consumer-price-index-inflation-federal-reserve-1851716425?_gl=1*kobuln*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzgwMDYuNDQuMC4w" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">inflation</a></span> and <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://qz.com/glp-1-drugs-grocery-bill-spending-retail-food-2025-1851731159?_gl=1*kobuln*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzgwMDYuNDQuMC4w&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://qz.com/glp-1-drugs-grocery-bill-spending-retail-food-2025-1851731159?_gl=1*kobuln*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzgwMDYuNDQuMC4w" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">rising food prices</a></span> — remains uncertain.</p><p>Starbucks’ Red Cup Day in November, during which the company handed out <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://www.placer.ai/blog/starbucks-red-cup-day-makes-a-comeback&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://www.placer.ai/blog/starbucks-red-cup-day-makes-a-comeback" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">reusable red cups</a></span>, saw a 42.4% increase in foot traffic compared to the previous months, according to analytics firm Placeri.ai. This success, along with <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://qz.com/starbucks-new-items-value-wars-mcdonalds-2025-1851733465?_gl=1*kobuln*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzgwMDYuNDQuMC4w&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://qz.com/starbucks-new-items-value-wars-mcdonalds-2025-1851733465?_gl=1*kobuln*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzgwMDYuNDQuMC4w" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">recent menu additions</a></span> like new espresso options and vegan-friendly falafel wraps, could help it compete in the ongoing “<span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://qz.com/mcdonalds-chilis-taco-bell-winners-losers-casual-dining-1851728895?_gl=1*kobuln*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzgwMDYuNDQuMC4w&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://qz.com/mcdonalds-chilis-taco-bell-winners-losers-casual-dining-1851728895?_gl=1*kobuln*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzgwMDYuNDQuMC4w" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">value wars</a></span>.” </p><p>But in 2024, the Starbucks fell short of attracting consumers both in the U.S. and in China, its second-largest market. In December, the company announced it would <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://qz.com/starbucks-paid-parental-leave-18-weeks-retail-workers-1851721988?_gl=1*klf80n*_ga*NjQwMDk3NjE0LjE3MTMxODc3NjE.*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI3NjcxNy4xMDIuMS4xNzM2Mjc5Mjk1LjU1LjAuMA..&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://qz.com/starbucks-paid-parental-leave-18-weeks-retail-workers-1851721988?_gl=1*klf80n*_ga*NjQwMDk3NjE0LjE3MTMxODc3NjE.*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI3NjcxNy4xMDIuMS4xNzM2Mjc5Mjk1LjU1LjAuMA.." target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">triple its parental leave</a></span> for baristas who work a least 20 hours per week. Meanwhile, in China, Starbucks hired its <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://qz.com/starbucks-china-business-appoints-chief-growth-officer-1851721861?_gl=1*kobuln*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzgwMDYuNDQuMC4w&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://qz.com/starbucks-china-business-appoints-chief-growth-officer-1851721861?_gl=1*kobuln*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzgwMDYuNDQuMC4w" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">first-ever chief growth officer</a></span> as it looks to collaborate with entertainment brands to attract customers that have flocked to chains like Luckin’ Coffee. </p><p>The Minnie Mouse collaboration could attract some traffic, but like McDonald’s “<span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://qz.com/mcdonalds-collectors-meal-promo-big-arch-5-meal-deal-1851615552?_gl=1*g780ji*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzgwMDYuNDQuMC4w&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://qz.com/mcdonalds-collectors-meal-promo-big-arch-5-meal-deal-1851615552?_gl=1*g780ji*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzgwMDYuNDQuMC4w" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Collector’s Cup</a></span>” promotion, which saw customers <span><a data-ga="[[&quot;Embedded Url&quot;,&quot;External link&quot;,&quot;https://qz.com/mconalds-happy-meal-cups-resale-ebay-mercari-1851624021?_gl=1*g780ji*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzgwMDYuNDQuMC4w&quot;,{&quot;metric25&quot;:1}]]" href="https://qz.com/mconalds-happy-meal-cups-resale-ebay-mercari-1851624021?_gl=1*g780ji*_ga*MTkzNTUxMDgwMy4xNzI0MjQ2NjI3*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczNjI2MjEyMS42Mi4xLjE3MzYyNzgwMDYuNDQuMC4w" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">reselling the cups for up $100</a></span> on third-party websites like eBay, Starbucks’ boost might be short-lived. The company will need more than novelty items to truly address its current challenges.</p><p><em>This story originally appeared on Quartz, our sister site, on January 7.</em></p><p><em>.</em></p></div></div>]]></content:encoded>
